rbnAtm2MIB.name: rbnAtm2MIB
rbnAtm2MIB.contactinfo: Redback Networks, Inc. Postal: 300 Holger Way San Jose, CA 95134 USA Phone: +1 408 750 5000 Fax: +1 408 750 5599 E-mail: mib-info@redback.com
rbnAtm2MIB.description: The MIB for instrumenting statistics associated with ATM VPL and VCL beyond those instrumented by ATM2-MIB.

rbnAtm2VplStatTable.name: rbnAtm2VplStatTable
rbnAtm2VplStatTable.description: This table provides a collection of statistics objects of a VPL.

rbnAtm2VplStatEntry.name: rbnAtm2VplStatEntry
rbnAtm2VplStatEntry.description: Each entry in this table represents a VPL.

rbnAtm2VplOutPktDrops.name: rbnAtm2VplOutPktDrops
rbnAtm2VplOutPktDrops.description: The number of transmit packets dropped by this VPL.

rbnAtm2VclStatTable.name: rbnAtm2VclStatTable
rbnAtm2VclStatTable.description: This table provides a collection of statistics objects of a VCL.

rbnAtm2VclStatEntry.name: rbnAtm2VclStatEntry
rbnAtm2VclStatEntry.description: Each entry in this table represents a VCL.

rbnAtm2VclOutPktDrops.name: rbnAtm2VclOutPktDrops
rbnAtm2VclOutPktDrops.description: The number of transmit packets dropped by this VCL.

rbnAtm2Aal5VclStatTable.name: rbnAtm2Aal5VclStatTable
rbnAtm2Aal5VclStatTable.description: This table provides a collection of auxiliary objects providing AAL5 configuration and performance statistics of a VCL.

rbnAtm2Aal5VclStatEntry.name: rbnAtm2Aal5VclStatEntry
rbnAtm2Aal5VclStatEntry.description: Each entry in this table represents a VCL.

rbnAtm2Aal5VclOutPktDrops.name: rbnAtm2Aal5VclOutPktDrops
rbnAtm2Aal5VclOutPktDrops.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs received for transmission on the AAL5 VCC at the interface identified by the ifIndex which were chosen to be dropped even though no errors had been detected to prevent their being transmitted. One possible reason for dropping such a PDU could be a lack of available space on the interface output queue.

rbnAtm2Compliance.name: rbnAtm2Compliance
rbnAtm2Compliance.description: The compliance statement for SNMP entities which implement the Redback ATM2 MIB.

rbnAtm2CommonStatsGroup.name: rbnAtm2CommonStatsGroup
rbnAtm2CommonStatsGroup.description: A collection of objects providing supplemental VPL/VCL information beyond that supplied by IETF standards-track MIBs

rbnAtm2HostGroup.name: rbnAtm2HostGroup
rbnAtm2HostGroup.description: A collection of objects providing supplemental AAL5 VCL information beyond that supplied by IETF standards-track MIBs
